<Weakness xmlns="http://cwe.mitre.org/cwe-7" xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" ID="307" Name="Improper Restriction of Excessive Authentication Attempts" Abstraction="Base" Structure="Simple" Status="Draft" Diagram="/data/images/CWE-307-Diagram.png">
         <Description>The product does not implement sufficient measures to prevent multiple failed authentication attempts within a short time frame.</Description>
